<style>
    .terms-policy {
        margin-top: 140px;
    }

    .terms-policy-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0px 20px;
    }

    .terms-policy a {
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 2px;
        transition: .4s ease all;
        font-family: var(--aspekta);
    }

    .terms-policy a:hover {
        cursor: pointer;
        color: var(--orange);
    }

    .terms-policy ul,
    .terms-policy ol {
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
    }

    .terms-policy ul {
        list-style: square;
    }

    .terms-policy p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-family: var(--aspekta);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 150%;
        margin-bottom: 20px;

    }

    .heading p {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2.88px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .terms-policy h2,
    .terms-policy h3,
    .terms-policy h4,
    .terms-policy h5,
    .terms-policy h6 {
        padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .terms-policy ul li::marker {
        font-size: 12px;
    }

    .terms-policy h1 {
        font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 62px);
    }

    .terms-policy h2 {
        font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 52px);
    }

    .terms-policy h3 {
        font-size: clamp(22px, 5vw, 36px);
    }

    .terms-policy h4 {
        font-size: clamp(20px, 5vw, 28px);
    }

    .terms-policy h5 {
        font-size: clamp(20px, 5vw, 26px);
    }

    .terms-policy h6 {
        font-size: clamp(18px, 5vw, 24px);
    }

    li {
        font-family: var(--aspekta);
        line-height: 130%;
        font-size: 16px;
    }

    .terms-policy-content{
        padding-top: 40px;
    }
    @media (max-width:767px) {

        p,
        li,
        a {
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .heading p{
            font-size: 10px;
        }
    }
</style>
<section class="terms-policy">
    <div class="terms-policy-container">
        <div class="terms-policy-in">
            <div class="heading">
                {% if section.settings.heading != blank %}
                    <h1>{{ section.settings.heading }}</h1>
                {% endif %}
                {% if section.settings.last_modified != blank %}
                    <p>{{ section.settings.last_modified }}</p>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="terms-policy-content">
                {{ section.settings.terms_policy_content }}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
    "name": "Privacy Policy",
    "settings": [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "id": "heading",
            "label": "Heading",
            "default": "Privacy Policy"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "id": "last_modified",
            "label": "Last modified text",
            "default": "Last modified : February 2025"
        },
        {
            "type": "html",
            "id": "terms_policy_content",
            "label": "Terms policy content",
            "default": "<h2>Hello, this is terms and condition heading</h2><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Nunc cras lacus aliquet posuere facilisis. Amet pellentesque viverra eu faucibus justo diam. Condimentum auctor ipsum urna pharetra eget.</p><h3>Title</h3><h4>This is h4</h4><p>Feugiat in erat accumsan quis ornare posuere adipiscing aliquam ligula. Elementum vulputate eu fermentum platea fringilla.</p><h5>This is h5</h5><p>Feugiat in erat accumsan quis ornare posuere adipiscing aliquam ligula. Elementum vulputate eu fermentum platea fringilla.</p><h6>This is h6</h6><p>Feugiat in erat accumsan quis ornare posuere adipiscing aliquam ligula. Elementum vulputate eu fermentum platea fringilla.</p><ul><li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.</li><li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.</li><li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.</li></ul><ol><li>Omnis itaque, dolorem maiores pariatur temporibus molestias quidem autem?</li><li>Omnis itaque, dolorem maiores pariatur temporibus molestias quidem autem?</li><li>Omnis itaque, dolorem maiores pariatur temporibus molestias quidem autem?</li></ol><a href=\"#!\">click me boss</a><p>Omnis itaque, dolorem maiores pariatur temporibus molestias quidem autem? Rem dolore, <a href=\"#!\">Click me boss</a> soluta, praesentium iusto magni natus.</p>"
        }
    ],
    "presets": [
        {
            "name": "Privacy Policy"
        }
    ]
}
{% endschema %}
